  "contents": "<div class=\"content markitup-box\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t共匪中国风声鹤唳草木皆兵，近日居然对 “<b>狗</b>” 大发雷霆，举国声讨！据说是某笑话演员？某日当场练嘴时谈到其膝下野狗两条，“<b>作风过硬，能打胜仗</b>”。于是共匪窝巢上下，群情激愤怒火冲天，说是“侮辱”了共军兵将，罪当处死！<br/>\r\n此罪何来？原来共匪巢穴内外，常以吹捧自家匪军兵丁“解放军”为 “作风过硬，能打胜仗” 云云，舔脸无耻，肉麻至极。今日被相近场合与狗并论，不禁暴怒如雷，号称各军兵种纷纷奋起，不接受道歉，只需看抓捕杀头枪决，必须立即执行！于是举凡共匪大陆上下，一片声讨叫嚣，全境从此不许发笑！从此谁笑，谁侮辱解放军 “作风过硬，能打胜仗”，必坐牢枪决，全体必须跪！高呼解放军英勇杀敌，是奴才亲爹，模样英俊美丽器宇轩昂：<br/>\n<br/>\n<b><a href=\"https://pincong.rocks/article/38242\" title=\"https://pincong.rocks/article/38242\">乱世笑林</a></b><br/>\n<a href=\"https://pincong.rocks/article/item_id-1039761__notification_id-858633\" title=\"https://pincong.rocks/article/item_id-1039761__notification_id-858633\">共匪军队韩战被澳军俘虏时操像</a>    <a href=\"https://pincong.rocks/video/7738\" title=\"https://pincong.rocks/video/7738\">共匪兵丁被台湾国军俘虏后操像</a> <a href=\"https://pincong.rocks/article/58427\" title=\"https://pincong.rocks/article/58427\">北京女记者痛斥共匪大陆G点成灾一碰就飞</a><br/>\n<a class=\"placeholder\" href=\"url/img/aHR0cHM6Ly9pLmltZ3VyLmNvbS90YUpxUWJZLmpwZWc\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"https://i.imgur.com/taJqQbY.jpeg\"><img alt=\"https://i.imgur.com/taJqQbY.jpeg\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://i.imgur.com/taJqQbY.jpeg\" style=\"max-width:100%\"/></a><br/>\n<a class=\"placeholder\" href=\"url/img/aHR0cHM6Ly9pLmltZ3VyLmNvbS96Zkk2TFRLLnBuZw\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"https://i.imgur.com/zfI6LTK.png\"><img alt=\"https://i.imgur.com/zfI6LTK.png\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://i.imgur.com/zfI6LTK.png\" style=\"max-width:100%\"/></a><br/>\n<a class=\"placeholder\" href=\"url/img/aHR0cHM6Ly9pLmltZ3VyLmNvbS81VXdJYTZ0LmpwZw\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"https://i.imgur.com/5UwIa6t.jpg\"><img alt=\"https://i.imgur.com/5UwIa6t.jpg\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://i.imgur.com/5UwIa6t.jpg\" style=\"max-width:100%\"/></a><br/>\n<a class=\"placeholder\" href=\"url/img/aHR0cHM6Ly9pLmltZ3VyLmNvbS9xcmZIaXFDLmpwZw\" rel=